body.name: Sooez 14 Pack Mesh Zipper Pouch Bags, A4 Letter Size, Zipper Bags with Label Pocket, Waterproof Zipper Pouches for Classroom Organization, Board Game Storage, Document Bag for Office School Supplies
deliveryMessages: FREE delivery Thursday, February 22 on orders shipped by Amazon over $35. Order within 2 hrs 50 mins
features: Zipper Pouches with Label Pockets: 14 Packs, 13.3"x9.4" mesh zipper bags in 7 colors (2pcs for each color). An additional label pocket helps you more easily and quickly to find what you need, which makes our storage bags stand out better than other mesh bags.

Premium Quality & Durable: The plastic mesh pouch is made of high-quality PVC material, thicker than similar products, and durable for everyday use. The metal zipper glides smoothly, which is sturdy and not easy to fall off. Waterproof bags keep your items from water spills and dirt.

Simple Storage: Are you getting in trouble with a jumbled mess? These large capacity bags make school and office supplies storage easier and help things organized and sorted at work and home. A perfect space saver to get rid of bulky boxes.

Translucent Document Bags: The mesh bags are semi-transparent enough to see what's inside while preventing privacy leaks. These translucent file bags with the label outside facilitate document positioning and make finding items easy without unzipping.

Wide Applications: It’s an ideal choice for class organization, office supplies, puzzles, board games storage, travel storage, art supplies, cosmetics, bills, receipts, and more. Convenient and portable for transporting things back and forth to school or work.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Games boxes be gone
reviews.reviewText: I’ve seen these bags go viral, and there’s a good reason for that! These bags have a lot of my children to be able to clean up their own games without frustration. It has also allowed me to have less storage for the same amount of items as they are stackable and able to be placed side by side. The only downfall for these bags is they don’t necessarily sit a game board. But they are perfect for games with multiple small pieces such as matching, cooties, cards. A little Lipo place in the front allows you to place a picture of the game or a label of the game. I also love that their color coordinated so I can put mine games in one color, multiple player games in another and my children know where to look for which games.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for me
reviews.reviewText: I used these to organize my craft supplies, children’s toys, make-up, self-care items by categories.I used to have a bunch of bins but some things didn’t require so much space.since they came in different colors I can quickly grab the color that I need and love that I can change the label easily.I also use it for our medical supply kit where we keep medicines as well.
